{"tid":2082722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"近年出現一種騙案叫搶單","createTime":"2020-06-28T09:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T19:05:33.000Z","uid":34960,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"898d05524188b44fb4ee33e55952bc8ce95c6aeb","tid":2082722,"uid":34960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:10:55.000Z","msg":"想做/做緊搶單既人留意！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講個個app都係呃你錢，但我就親身經歷過一個叫天品雲倉既呃錢搶單app事件<br />\n<br />\n個app會同你講你要入錢買貨，然後賣家就會退返你俾既錢你，再加一定既傭金<br />\n<br />\ne. g. 件貨1000 蚊，你個account要有最少1000 買我起件貨 賣家會退返1001蚊俾你，你就賺左一蚊<br />\n<br />\n一開始確係可以俾你攞錢賺錢，<br />\n到做左一個零月呢就開始有個活動，入幾多就回贈50%俾你，期間無得攞錢。<br />\n<br />\n到活動完左都係攞唔到錢，各種原因話咩帳號異常呀，要你入返舊錢先可以攞錢<br />\n<br />\n然後到兜唔到admin就踢哂所有人，上線又del哂所有同我地既對話record<br />\n<br />\n已經有好多同類騙案架啦，下面有d圖俾大家參考下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoWRQEe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoWRQEe.jpg&h=25980fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w4aLaEk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw4aLaEk.jpg&h=55d81440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTAy3Zp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTAy3Zp.jpg&h=890f21cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MC81tq7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMC81tq7.jpg&h=cf09b221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPXmtra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPXmtra.jpg&h=29a53f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dox5U6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDox5U6e.jpg&h=c54e8986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCrKrcW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCrKrcW.jpg&h=03f87f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PK79CjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k